  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 17 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Demonstrators recovered 17 million rupees from the Presidential Palace and handed it over to the police",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police media reported in a statement that the protesters handed over 17 million rupees found in the presidential palace yesterday.",
        "The President's House located in the Colombo Fort was besieged by rioters after the people protested against the government on Saturday 9th yesterday.",
        "After this, the demonstrators entered the Presidential Palace and seized a large amount of money in a secret place in a room allegedly used by Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "In this case, after the protestors handed over the money to the Superintendent of Police who was in charge of duties in that area, the money was handed over to the Fort Police Station.",
        "Subsequently, in a report published by the police, it has been reported in the police media report that 17 million rupees have been recovered from the presidential palace and handed over to him."
      ],
